I am up for a war..but since many Forum boards are strictly for guild use.. how bout one on the Mythical Odyssey board.  If someone wants to start up on there I am all for it.  But...please remember the below ...which I also posted for announcment on each page.<br>
<br>
PLEASE, fill out ezboard profiles...state if your character is MORTAL or IMMORTAL. If immortal, please state powers so that they will be recognized. You MUST have those powers in profile to be recognize if you are not an "a" typical myth god/dess. This helps other's know who you are and what you can do. But, please note...there is to be no killing off of other's  characters. You may injure or place a spell on another character. But that character chooses how long or how devistating the wound or spell is to their OWN character. Attacks and such can be fun...but remember to allow the mun's to control their character in the end. <br>
<br>
On the MO board...guilds can mix without anyone jumping in and saying NO NO.  I as Admin of the board and so payer of the fees to keep it (LOL)...say so.  That way.. you can mix up and play without hurting any guild rules.  The only thing is please fill out your profile so we know WHO THE HECK ARE YOU AND WHAT CAN YOU DO. The  only exception to this rule..are ACTUAL known gods from myth.  OK? ok...... <br>
<br>
